  2→//! Integration Tests for Serval
  3→//!
  4→//! Spawns actual server binaries and tests them end-to-end.
  5→//! Tests cover HTTP and HTTPS scenarios including TLS termination,
  6→//! TLS origination, and mixed HTTP/HTTPS backend pools.
